flutter_xlog packages a Flutter FFI bridge for Tencent mars xlog.

Tencent mars is distributed by Tencent under the license terms published with
the upstream mars project. Before publishing this package, verify that the
bundled Android shared libraries and iOS xcframework may be redistributed under
your chosen package license and release process.

This package also includes Android C++ runtime artifacts required by the bundled
native libraries. Verify redistributable status for every bundled binary before
uploading to pub.dev.
